        <updateDate>2006-02-22T18:35:39Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ Youth Exchange Support Act of 2006- Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) increase, from $50 to $200 per month, the tax deduction for the expenses of certain students living in a taxpayer's household; and (2) provide an inflation adjustment, beginning in 2007, for such amount.]]></text>
      </summary>
